author: jcompagner
msg: Fix for the new onInitialize code.

MarkupContainer initialize() was creating loops in loops in loops because the entry point (initialize method) also created a visitior and calls then the entry point (initialize) again on those children (including children of the children). This does go wrong (or slow) in an exponential way.
